---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '@components/Hero.astro';
import Section from '@components/Section.astro';
import Button from '@components/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Cremation Services"
  description="Professional cremation services for funeral homes across Northwest Ohio, Southern Michigan, and Northeast Indiana. Handled with dignity and respect."
>
  <Hero
    title="Cremation Services"
    subtitle="Professional cremation support for funeral homes and their families"
    height="medium"
  />

  <Section padding="large">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Fox Mortuary Services provides comprehensive cremation services for funeral homes
          throughout our tri-state service area. We understand the importance of handling
          each case with dignity, respect, and professionalism.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-forest-800 mb-6">
          Our Cremation Services
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          As part of our commitment to serving funeral homes and industry professionals, we
          offer complete cremation support services. Every aspect of the cremation process
          is handled with the same level of care and attention to detail that families and
          funeral directors expect.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-forest-50 p-8 rounded-lg mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-forest-800 mb-4">
            What We Provide
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-gold-600 mr-3 mt-1">✓</span>
              <span>Professional handling and preparation prior to cremation</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-gold-600 mr-3 mt-1">✓</span>
              <span>Complete coordination with funeral homes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-gold-600 mr-3 mt-1">✓</span>
              <span>Respectful, dignified cremation process</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-gold-600 mr-3 mt-1">✓</span>
              <span>Transportation and removal services</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-gold-600 mr-3 mt-1">✓</span>
              <span>Documentation and certificate preparation</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-forest-800 mt-12 mb-6">
          Professional Standards
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          All cremation services are performed according to the highest industry standards
          and regulations. Our experienced staff ensures that every case receives the
          professional attention it deserves, maintaining the trust that funeral homes
          place in us.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          With over 30 years of experience serving the funeral industry, Fox Mortuary
          Services has developed proven procedures and protocols that ensure consistency,
          reliability, and peace of mind for the funeral homes we serve.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gold-50 border-l-4 border-gold-500 p-8 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-forest-800 mb-4">
            Serving Funeral Homes
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            As a licensed funeral trade establishment, Fox Mortuary Services works exclusively
            with funeral homes and industry professionals, not the general public. This
            business-to-business approach allows us to provide specialized support services
            tailored to the needs of funeral directors.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Our cremation services integrate seamlessly with your funeral home operations,
            providing reliable support when you need it most.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-forest-800 mt-12 mb-6">
          Service Area
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We provide cremation services to funeral homes throughout:
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-forest-500 pl-4">
            <p class="font-semibold text-forest-800">Northwest Ohio</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-forest-500 pl-4">
            <p class="font-semibold text-forest-800">Southern Michigan</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-forest-500 pl-4">
            <p class="font-semibold text-forest-800">Northeast Indiana</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-forest-800 mb-6">
          Questions About Our Cremation Services?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">
          Contact us to discuss how we can support your funeral home with professional
          cremation services.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <Button href="/contact/" variant="primary" size="large">
            Contact Us
          </Button>
          <Button href="/services/" variant="outline" size="large">
            View All Services
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
